        <mxCell id="-mbjhE5D9MRw-dl7g4Tc-1" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;" value="&lt;b&gt;Advantages of terraform&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;can be used in multiple cloud providers&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;can be used in hybrid cloud set up&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;can track our infra using terraform i.e. we dont need to login to cloud provider, we can simply login terraform and check state file&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;we can automate changes&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;except state file we can keep all the config files in git repository and hence we can collaborate with our peers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;standardize configuration&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;takes re confirmation while applying&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
